    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion for weekend drives and has always been treated with the respect a car like this deserves. It\u2019s in wonderful shape overall\u2014sure, it\u2019s got a tiny bit of character from the road here and there, but it still shines like a diamond and runs like a dream. I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance because I truly love this machine. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth, spirited ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure, come take a look! I\u2019d love to see it go to another enthusiast who will appreciate it as much as I have.",
