    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted specimen optimized for the discerning driver. The heart of this machine maintains exceptional cylinder compression and rock-solid oil pressure, even at operating temperature. I\u2019ve ensured the valvetrain remains silent through rigorous maintenance cycles, utilizing only high-shear synthetic lubricants. The chassis benefits from refreshed bushings and a dialed-in alignment that eliminates scrub and enhances turn-in response. Thermal management is rock-solid thanks to a high-efficiency cooling system overhaul, ensuring the engine stays well within its power band during spirited sessions. The drivetrain is tight, with crisp engagement and zero lash in the differential. This is a high-integrity build where the mechanical sympathy of the previous ownership is evident in every gear change.",
